 src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成日遊車河自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eabb0464b678c86895a7c325e68826bc5930774","tid":2199900,"uid":82708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"假日車無問題<br />\n錢係人哋嘅鍾意點用架車都得<br />\n<br />\n不過成日話寧願返工搭的士／uber 都唔揸車嘅<br />\n一定係好少返工繁忙時間(08:00 - 08:20)搭的士／uber<br />\n你可以落街後5 分鐘內叫到或者截到車已經係贏家<br />\n結論搭的士都可以趕頭趕命, 不如自己揸車輕輕鬆鬆落樓開車<br />\n時間快慢自己控制<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係市區 市中心大路截車 見到巴士小巴多過的士"},{"pid":"7ff05954cbe02a36fd9219e3d73668eb2552e384","tid":2199900,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b566eebabd39203db46970e337a804e15666e8","tid":2199900,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10ac713dc96816e7a4b46fbc36db263d51e62c0a","tid":2199900,"uid":215611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"有車有閪屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"撚有"},{"pid":"04897f28cec7aecfa35155eca78ce0607065930a","tid":2199900,"uid":82708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5ca74ad8407bb59a4020ee08b97ea136c93d603","tid":2199900,"uid":353358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"我有時會特登由觀塘渣去屯公、天水圍、青朗、吐路港、西沙、西貢 1個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有車你鐘意點玩都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意 呢條路線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果可以加埋 三仔 南灣 青馬 入東涌 機場 仲正"}]}